{"raw": null, "markup": "markdown", "html": "", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2013-09-26T17:02:15.531344+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Keaton Burns", "uuid": "{3d3e64f1-bf12-45df-b655-4543d8fb34c4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3d3e64f1-bf12-45df-b655-4543d8fb34c4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3d3e64f1-bf12-45df-b655-4543d8fb34c4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:e31a7835-5317-4dfa-8551-f32a06f40279/40f33f99-2b75-4a17-a8c2-07c8d74c7480/128"}}, "nickname": "kburns", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:e31a7835-5317-4dfa-8551-f32a06f40279"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 6228732}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/dedalus-project/dedalus/issues/15/comments/6262722.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/dedalus-project/dedalus/issues/15#comment-6262722"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/dedalus-project/dedalus/issues/15.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 15, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/dedalus-project/dedalus.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/dedalus-project/dedalus"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{1dc39ab6-2798-450d-af2f-e976f94b5794}ts=2009435"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "dedalus", "full_name": "dedalus-project/dedalus", "uuid": "{1dc39ab6-2798-450d-af2f-e976f94b5794}"}, "title": "Liveplot animation vs frames"}, "content": {"raw": "Keaton,\n     Thanks for catching that!  I can confirm that it's working on my 10.8 mac.\n\nInterestingly, the liveplot windows always appear in the background, behind all other windows.  Is that deliberate, or should I look into ways to pop them to the front of the display stack?", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Keaton,\n     Thanks for catching that!  I can confirm that it's working on my 10.8 mac.</p>\n<p>Interestingly, the liveplot windows always appear in the background, behind all other windows.  Is that deliberate, or should I look into ways to pop them to the front of the display stack?</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2013-09-30T05:26:54.539690+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Benjamin Brown", "uuid": "{7ccecdb3-3639-4001-8249-060e80320bda}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B7ccecdb3-3639-4001-8249-060e80320bda%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B7ccecdb3-3639-4001-8249-060e80320bda%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:0696c4b9-e94c-41ac-82be-62ad4f0ec571/8bc6f4da-871a-48b1-88ea-998663d18142/128"}}, "nickname": "Benjamin Brown", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:0696c4b9-e94c-41ac-82be-62ad4f0ec571"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 6262722}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/dedalus-project/dedalus/issues/15/comments/6273622.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/dedalus-project/dedalus/issues/15#comment-6273622"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/dedalus-project/dedalus/issues/15.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 15, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/dedalus-project/dedalus.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/dedalus-project/dedalus"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{1dc39ab6-2798-450d-af2f-e976f94b5794}ts=2009435"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "dedalus", "full_name": "dedalus-project/dedalus", "uuid": "{1dc39ab6-2798-450d-af2f-e976f94b5794}"}, "title": "Liveplot animation vs frames"}, "content": {"raw": "For me it opens behind the terminal window, but in front of anything else I have open.  I'm not sure this is something we can easily affect -- the only thing I've been able to find about it is this old matplotlib issue, but it doesn't really look like it went anywhere:\n\nhttps://github.com/matplotlib/matplotlib/issues/596", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>For me it opens behind the terminal window, but in front of anything else I have open.  I'm not sure this is something we can easily affect -- the only thing I've been able to find about it is this old matplotlib issue, but it doesn't really look like it went anywhere:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/matplotlib/matplotlib/issues/596\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://github.com/matplotlib/matplotlib/issues/596</a></p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2013-09-30T15:28:51.800081+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Keaton Burns", "uuid": "{3d3e64f1-bf12-45df-b655-4543d8fb34c4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3d3e64f1-bf12-45df-b655-4543d8fb34c4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3d3e64f1-bf12-45df-b655-4543d8fb34c4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:e31a7835-5317-4dfa-8551-f32a06f40279/40f33f99-2b75-4a17-a8c2-07c8d74c7480/128"}}, "nickname": "kburns", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:e31a7835-5317-4dfa-8551-f32a06f40279"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 6273622}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/dedalus-project/dedalus/issues/15/comments/7674547.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/dedalus-project/dedalus/issues/15#comment-7674547"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/dedalus-project/dedalus/issues/15.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 15, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/dedalus-project/dedalus.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/dedalus-project/dedalus"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{1dc39ab6-2798-450d-af2f-e976f94b5794}ts=2009435"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "dedalus", "full_name": "dedalus-project/dedalus", "uuid": "{1dc39ab6-2798-450d-af2f-e976f94b5794}"}, "title": "Liveplot animation vs frames"}, "content": {"raw": "Quick note that the plotting scripts referenced here were moved to a separate examples repository as of commit c5873d0.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Quick note that the plotting scripts refe